reviewText: A blast from the past so worth it.
It was still in it's original packaging. The DVD's have been running very smoothly. I am highly satisfied.
the boxes arrived in good shape but one of the dvd have some scratch on it.
Rip off, since you can buy all of the exact same set individually at a lower price.
Love Dragon Ball and a huge fan. Got this box set for a real good deal. It complete my whole series with dbz and dbzgt
